[ 23390] By: nicholas                              on 2004/10/19  19:35:22
        Log: Integrate:
             [ 23331]
             Subject:  Re: [perl #31586] utime does not reach expectations [PATCH]
             From:  LAUN Wolfgang <wolfgang.laun@alcatel.at>
             Date:  Fri, 17 Sep 2004 14:01:11 +0200
