[ 23314] By: nicholas                              on 2004/09/10  10:24:09
        Log: Integrate:
             [ 23146]
             Subject: [PATCH] Mention common dynaloader errors in perldiag.pod
             From: "Jos I. Boumans" <kane@dwim.org>
